OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a dry and warm day
OL,6,Fwith some hazy sunny spells developing
OL,7,Fby the afternoon. Brisk westerly winds
OL,8,Facross the north and west.
OL,9,
OL,10,CTonight:FIncreasingly cloudy this
OL,11,Fevening with the chance of light and
OL,12,Fpatchy rain, perhaps briefly turning
OL,13,Fheavier. Later, clearer spells and
OL,14,Fisolated showers develop, accompanied
OL,15,Fby freshening winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
