OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FRather cloudy at first, with
OL,6,Fpatchy light rain spreading southeast
OL,7,Fduring the morning. Then turning drier
OL,8,Fand brighter in the afternoon with a
OL,9,Ffew light scattered showers. Fresh
OL,10,Fwinds easing.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FBright
OL,13,For sunny spells on Sunday with the odd
OL,14,Fshower, but many places dry. Fairly
OL,15,Funsettled and changeable later Monday
OL,16,Fand Tuesday with the risk of rain or
OL,17,Fshowers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
